Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.52,0:00:04.83,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}As times{\rHonorifics - Narration Off} chan{\r}ge,\Ndifficult cases increase in number!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.83,0:00:06.90,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Today's stage is a villa!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.90,0:00:09.23,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}A black shadow beneath a{\rHonorifics - Narration Off} chan{\r}delier!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.23,0:00:11.07,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.07,0:00:13.27,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.27,0:00:15.55,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.88,0:00:20.55,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Created by\NGosho Aoyama\N"Detective Conan"\NSerialized in Shogakukan's\N"Weekly Shonen Sunday"
