Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.80,0:01:41.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.35,0:01:52.80,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Reika Yotsui (24)\NDaughter of Yotsui Group President
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.18,0:01:55.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy 24th birthday, Reika!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.95,0:01:57.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.85,0:02:06.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I humbly thank you all for being here today!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.10,0:02:11.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,May both she and the Yotsui Group\Ncontinue to prosper!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.37,0:02:15.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop eating like a pig! You're embarrassing me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.74,0:02:18.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on! You guys should eat too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.61,0:02:21.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not often you see food like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.15,0:02:27.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta love that vintage wine!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.15,0:02:33.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, allow me to introduce our special guest!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.06,0:02:35.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The great Kogoro Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.56,0:02:39.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Could I get a box to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.56,0:02:41.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be a crime to waste any!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.90,0:02:44.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.37,0:02:48.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! The modern-day Kogoro Akechi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.68,0:02:50.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're too kind!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.37,0:02:55.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is, he helped my daughter just yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.41,0:02:57.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it was nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.50,0:02:59.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do for her?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.15,0:03:03.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a tough little case.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.15,0:03:05.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A tough case?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.06,0:03:07.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard about that, Detective Mouri!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.92,0:03:12.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You found Miss Reika's dog, Bubble{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.50,0:03:14.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.70,0:03:19.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Ichieda!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.77,0:03:18.78,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Takashi Ichieda (26)\NCity Bank Fund Raising Department
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.87,0:03:23.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a real honor to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.59,0:03:25.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're too kind!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.08,0:03:29.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously. One look from those sharp eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.24,0:03:32.46,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuji Nikaido (27)\NAdvertising Agent
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.05,0:03:32.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,is all it takes to make a criminal confess.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.95,0:03:38.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The young lady was wise to choose you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.02,0:03:41.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough, you brown-nosers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.29,0:03:43.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mifune?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.13,0:03:49.14,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Takuya Mifune (26)\NPresident of Mifune Electronics
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.23,0:03:47.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know about you, but he seems
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.30,0:03:51.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,like a middle-aged airhead to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.90,0:03:52.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.88,0:03:54.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.24,0:03:55.74,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}He's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.74,0:03:58.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.11,0:04:04.53,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Osamu Gojo (24)\NGeneral Manager of Gojo Commerce
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.24,0:03:59.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.44,0:04:02.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I looked forward to today,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.11,0:04:05.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but he's not quite what I imagined...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.08,0:04:09.72,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.72,0:04:11.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Goes to show how childish you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.96,0:04:15.71,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Masashi Rokuda (40)\NYotsui Product Director
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.96,0:04:14.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't you heard the saying,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.73,0:04:16.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"Still waters run deep?"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.39,0:04:19.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Playing dumb to catch an opponent off guard
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.60,0:04:23.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,is a preferred tactic of all great detectives.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.20,0:04:25.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.30,0:04:27.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.60,0:04:29.67,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Some tactic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.67,0:04:32.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She anticipated that very fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.70,0:04:35.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's really something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.01,0:04:38.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Not to mention beautiful and refined!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.01,0:04:42.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder who won her heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.95,0:04:46.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I dunno, but he's gonna be one happy guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.32,0:04:50.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He gets to be the next head of the Yotsui Group!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.73,0:04:57.23,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Bathroom... Bathroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.23,0:04:59.90,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}This hallway sure is dark...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.90,0:05:02.61,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Why aren't the lights on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.61,0:05:04.27,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.18,0:05:08.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A closet?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.05,0:05:11.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shower room...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.92,0:05:14.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's the bathroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.05,0:05:17.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? The lights won't turn on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.69,0:05:20.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.11,0:05:22.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to use the bathroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.39,0:05:25.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The lights in this washroom don't work;
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.48,0:05:27.20,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Yone Nanao (64)\NYotsui Family Housekeeper
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.06,0:05:27.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,use the one across the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.60,0:05:29.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.27,0:05:34.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's odd. None of the lights around here work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.87,0:05:39.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I{\rHonorifics - Dialogue} chan{\r}ged them all just recently...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.24,0:05:41.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.55,0:05:45.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your daughter's car has a flat tire!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.05,0:05:46.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.22,0:05:48.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.17,0:05:51.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I take you home in my Ferrari?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.22,0:05:53.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'll take you in my Porsche!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.41,0:05:55.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How about my Benz?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.23,0:05:56.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.63,0:06:00.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All three of your cars have flats, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.37,0:06:05.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! They got my car too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.96,0:06:08.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mine, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.77,0:06:11.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell did this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.24,0:06:14.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad's rental car seems fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.35,0:06:15.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.45,0:06:18.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Six cars have flat tires.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.92,0:06:23.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The six of you will have to share cars with—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.09,0:06:25.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.12,0:06:27.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Today is my birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.69,0:06:30.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse to be stuffed into someone else's car!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.53,0:06:32.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, Reika...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.76,0:06:36.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm staying here with Yone tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.00,0:06:38.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come send for me in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.54,0:06:40.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll stay too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.24,0:06:42.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.21,0:06:43.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.27,0:06:46.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I, too, will spend the night and protect her
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.21,0:06:48.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,from these young wolves.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.58,0:06:52.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Good idea. I can rest easy with you on the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.15,0:06:54.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I leave her in your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.21,0:06:56.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Very good, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.06,0:07:02.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.56,0:07:08.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Fools. Her husband was already decided two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.80,0:07:12.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone left?! Then we should go—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.74,0:07:15.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't! Not until you sober up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.67,0:07:20.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Stay a little longer and tell us about your cases!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.24,0:07:22.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Splendid idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.25,0:07:26.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you say we all play cards?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.38,0:07:28.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Count me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.75,0:07:32.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Detective. I'll drive you home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.26,0:07:34.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Gimme your car keys.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.11,0:07:36.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, are you leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.53,0:07:42.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a pity. You were one of my candidate suitors.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.47,0:07:45.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I only came here to make sure the deal
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.40,0:07:51.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,between my company and your old man's goes through.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.11,0:07:53.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I'm not interested in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.74,0:07:55.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey now, Mifune!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.23,0:07:56.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.41,0:08:00.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. The fewer rivals the better.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.15,0:08:03.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So there you have it, Detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.02,0:08:04.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The key, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.42,0:08:06.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.89,0:08:11.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.32,0:08:13.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to leave, then leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.23,0:08:17.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But you can say goodbye to your deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.76,0:08:18.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.97,0:08:21.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yone. I'm going to{\rHonorifics - Dialogue} chan{\r}ge upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.05,0:08:23.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.71,0:08:26.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're nothing but caged birds.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.78,0:08:30.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't survive unless I feed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.48,0:08:35.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All you can do is chirp to soothe your owner!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.66,0:08:46.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You were all members of the same yacht club?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.33,0:08:50.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We used to sail around nearby islands in her boat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.73,0:08:53.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Those were great times!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.15,0:08:55.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They sure were.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.47,0:08:58.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Until the accident two years ago, anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.41,0:09:02.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Accident?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.93,0:09:04.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's old news.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.71,0:09:07.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We promised never to talk about it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.88,0:09:11.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She certainly is taking a long time...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.42,0:09:13.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you suppose she's doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.09,0:09:14.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.49,0:09:17.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't need her selfish attitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.16,0:09:23.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hasn't it been a little too long?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.37,0:09:24.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.70,0:09:28.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but could you take a look in her room?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.91,0:09:30.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Certainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.37,0:09:32.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go check the other rooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.74,0:09:34.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll go, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.06,0:09:34.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.91,0:09:36.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Same here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.51,0:09:39.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.98,0:09:42.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's strange. She isn't anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.52,0:09:46.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she left and got lost in the forest?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.52,0:09:52.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Our only choice is to split up\Nand search the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.26,0:09:55.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez. What a nuisance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.53,0:09:59.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.00,0:10:02.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.07,0:10:04.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Reika{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.07,0:10:07.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, where on earth did she go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.78,0:10:13.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's starting to come down!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.85,0:10:15.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.42,0:10:18.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go back for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.50,0:10:19.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.23,0:10:25.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.23,0:10:27.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that Nikaido{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.10,0:10:31.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey now, this is no time to be napping—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.50,0:10:45.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Nikaido! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.36,0:10:48.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use. He's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.30,0:10:50.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.44,0:10:52.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He was drowned.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.01,0:10:57.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone probably held his head in this fountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.34,0:10:59.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.25,0:11:01.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He was alive just a few minutes ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.92,0:11:05.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Meaning he was killed just now
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.99,0:11:09.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,by someone near this lodge!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.59,0:11:12.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's terrible! Who would do such a thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.73,0:11:17.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can think of someone suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.06,0:11:20.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The missing Reika-{\i1}ojosama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.67,0:11:25.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She would never!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.04,0:11:27.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, there's still no telling who.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.31,0:11:32.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,For all we know, she could be dead too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.15,0:11:34.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, let's call the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.95,0:11:36.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We can talk after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.92,0:11:39.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? The phones are out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.40,0:11:41.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, all of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.62,0:11:42.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How can that be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.81,0:11:45.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the killer's doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.16,0:11:47.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use my cell phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.96,0:11:52.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't bother. There's no phone reception out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.10,0:11:55.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Our only option now is to use the detective's car.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.67,0:12:00.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Someone could take it and get the police...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.34,0:12:07.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, now my tires are flat too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.35,0:12:13.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means someone wants to keep us here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.45,0:12:15.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.22,0:12:19.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll just have to wait until the cars come tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.43,0:12:21.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yone{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}. Please make us some coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.96,0:12:23.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Certainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.00,0:12:26.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.73,0:12:29.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mifune! Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.14,0:12:30.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The john.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.33,0:12:31.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll come too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.84,0:12:33.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.14,0:12:36.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get some towels from the washroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.74,0:12:39.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's dripping wet from the rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.16,0:12:40.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.95,0:12:45.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure know this place well, Mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.49,0:12:48.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We used to come here a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.43,0:12:55.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.09,0:12:56.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.50,0:12:58.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't find any sugar.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.77,0:13:02.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you check up there for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.10,0:13:04.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.38,0:13:17.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's none up here...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.08,0:13:20.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Here's some!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.09,0:13:24.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot we hoarded some five years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.66,0:13:27.03,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Is that sugar still any good?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.03,0:13:30.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, what kind of accident happened at the yacht club
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.03,0:13:31.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,two years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.73,0:13:36.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid. That's got nothing to do with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.34,0:13:40.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Before he was killed, Nikaido{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} said that
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.14,0:13:43.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Reika{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r}'s husband was decided two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.74,0:13:45.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.31,0:13:49.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It might have something to do with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.42,0:13:54.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Looks like we'll need you to talk
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.82,0:13:57.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,about this accident of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.82,0:14:02.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It happened during a storm. Most unfortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.63,0:14:04.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,On that day two years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.83,0:14:10.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,we landed on a small island and went off on our own.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.00,0:14:13.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Little did we know a storm was coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.17,0:14:16.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nearly everyone escaped back onto the boat,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.78,0:14:22.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,except for Nikaido and the young lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.32,0:14:27.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The island was so small that the full tide could submerge it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.39,0:14:32.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,One of us took a life raft to rescue her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.46,0:14:39.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We found them half a day later with life vests on,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.63,0:14:44.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but the person who went to get them was never seen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.27,0:14:48.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Until the drowned body was found three days later, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.81,0:14:52.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who was it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.28,0:14:54.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My granddaughter, Yaeko.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.54,0:14:55.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yone{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.98,0:15:00.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She sacrificed her life to rescue the young lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.15,0:15:02.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was probably worth it to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.69,0:15:05.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, your coffee's ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.93,0:15:07.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.33,0:15:14.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, first we need to find the young lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.97,0:15:20.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's split into two groups and check the house again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.41,0:15:24.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But since one of us could be the killer,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.18,0:15:26.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,let's make sure no one gets separated.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.65,0:15:30.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Good idea! It's safer if we watch each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.92,0:15:33.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll start once we're done here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.32,0:15:38.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At a time like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.55,0:15:41.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I'm suddenly sleepy...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.60,0:15:44.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be tired from all that's happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.13,0:15:48.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can take a nap on this sofa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.14,0:15:50.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stay with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.20,0:15:53.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.01,0:15:53.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Find her?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.89,0:15:54.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.74,0:15:55.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.64,0:15:56.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Not here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.94,0:15:59.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We've searched everywhere else but here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.68,0:16:02.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.15,0:16:03.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.72,0:16:05.82,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.82,0:16:08.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.12,0:16:12.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Reika{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.49,0:16:14.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd she disappear to?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.97,0:16:21.02,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Yaeko...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.77,0:16:24.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Not in here...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.77,0:16:26.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Or in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.71,0:16:30.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That takes care of the first floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.68,0:16:34.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She must be in the forest after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.08,0:16:36.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The power's out. Did something happen upstairs?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.58,0:16:37.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the circuit breaker?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.85,0:16:39.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Across from the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.52,0:16:46.79,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.79,0:16:48.09,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}It's close by!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.93,0:16:53.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who shut off the power?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.12,0:16:56.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We just got here...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.14,0:16:58.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was the killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.61,0:17:04.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,With us checking the house, they had nowhere to run,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.48,0:17:09.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so they cut the power and escaped out this window!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.48,0:17:11.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.35,0:17:13.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.50,0:17:14.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mifune!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.52,0:17:17.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! Stop them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.76,0:17:25.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! Where'd everyone go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.50,0:17:31.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,People often get lost in this forest...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.07,0:17:34.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yone{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}! What are you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.14,0:17:39.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I followed you when you scurried outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.01,0:17:40.68,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.68,0:17:42.91,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}That means Ran's all alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.45,0:17:48.35,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Who is this person?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.92,0:17:53.62,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Water?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.67,0:18:02.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.81,0:18:07.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.37,0:18:10.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ran! Wake up! Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.85,0:18:17.72,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Shin'ichi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.72,0:18:19.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.44,0:18:23.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone held my head underwater...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.16,0:18:29.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm glad you came, Shin'ichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.03,0:18:31.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran! Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.37,0:18:39.36,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Whew, she's just asleep. She had me scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.61,0:18:42.24,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}But that's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.24,0:18:45.71,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}This would normally wake a person up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.71,0:18:49.65,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Was there sleeping medicine in her coffee?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.65,0:18:52.09,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}But why Ran?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.09,0:18:57.19,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Huh? Didn't the old man leave this open?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.19,0:19:00.03,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}It's warm. How come?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.03,0:19:03.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Ran was attacked?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.26,0:19:06.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think someone gave her sleeping pills.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.77,0:19:08.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sleeping pills?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.97,0:19:13.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was probably in the coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.94,0:19:18.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you and Ran make the coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.55,0:19:21.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I would never-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.55,0:19:24.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't attack her-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.92,0:19:28.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,you were in the forest with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.96,0:19:33.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that she was attacked just because she was here
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.43,0:19:37.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,means that these might be random murders!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.90,0:19:45.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You were with her when the power went out, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.87,0:19:46.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.85,0:19:48.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did anything strange happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.98,0:19:52.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a warm breeze,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.95,0:19:56.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and then the lights went out...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.65,0:19:58.72,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}A breeze?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.72,0:20:01.12,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}The air conditioner?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.19,0:20:09.22,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}12:30! That's when the power went out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.40,0:20:20.71,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}All the air conditioners were set to go on at 12:30!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.71,0:20:25.15,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Now I know how the killer cut the lights!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.15,0:20:28.82,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}The killer {\i1}is{\i0} someone in this mansion!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.82,0:20:32.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too dangerous to stay in your room alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.75,0:20:35.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right, Mifune! It's past 4:00!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.56,0:20:38.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The cars will be here in three hours!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.43,0:20:42.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! I can't stay with you guys
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.26,0:20:44.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,when one of you might be a killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.87,0:20:49.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be in my room too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.10,0:20:53.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We'd all be safest together...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.13,0:21:14.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's 7:00...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.13,0:21:16.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to the bathroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.34,0:21:18.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I will too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.23,0:21:20.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.73,0:21:25.14,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Here is today's weather for the Kanto region.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.14,0:21:27.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They've been gone a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.13,0:21:31.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There are three of 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.28,0:21:34.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? What's with the coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.31,0:21:37.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They made it while I was in the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.38,0:21:39.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it would help wake us up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.15,0:21:44.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, I didn't drug it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.49,0:21:49.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,- Hot!\N- Where's the bathroom?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.63,0:21:51.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.60,0:21:55.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll leave a stain if we don't hurry—
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.50,0:23:49.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The two murders were done the exact same way!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.00,0:23:50.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.50,0:23:52.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.00,0:23:54.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichieda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} isn't the killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.97,0:23:58.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mifune{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}. You did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.58,0:24:01.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.05,0:24:03.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The same could be said about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.45,0:24:07.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one who could've done it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.03,0:24:13.99,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.99,0:24:19.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's Hint: Wet Shirt
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.27,0:24:21.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Next time is a sharp conclusion to the case!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.95,0:24:23.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}The killer was you!
